TITLE: Writing a Jest test for the sum function
DESCRIPTION: Example of a Jest test case for the previously defined sum function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jestjs/jest/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const sum = require('./sum');

test('adds 1 + 2 to equal 3', () => {
  expect(sum(1, 2)).toBe(3);
});
```

