TITLE: Writing a Basic Jest Test Case
DESCRIPTION: Creates a test file that imports the sum function and tests if it correctly adds 1 + 2 to equal 3 using Jest's expect and toBe matchers.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jestjs/jest/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-29.6/GettingStarted.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
