DESCRIPTION: Defines a Jest test that mounts the Link component, simulates mouse enter/leave events, and asserts that the snapshot output matches the expected rendering at each state. Uses react-test-renderer for rendering and simulating user interactions. This test checks both styling and event handler binding through snapshot outputs.
