SOURCE: https://github.com/jestjs/jest/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-29.4/GlobalAPI.md#2025-04-23_snippet_24

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
test.each([
  [1, 1, 2],
  [1, 2, 3],
  [2, 1, 3],
])('.add(%i, %i)', (a, b, expected) => {
  expect(a + b).toBe(expected);
});
```

