TITLE: Custom Jest Snapshot Path Resolver - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript CommonJS module exports a custom resolver object for Jest to map between test file paths and snapshot file paths. It provides resolveSnapshotPath and resolveTestPath functions, as well as a test path consistency check. This allows tests and snapshots to reside in parallel directory structures as required by project conventions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jestjs/jest/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-29.6/Configuration.md#2025-04-23_snippet_61

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
module.exports = {
  // resolves from test to snapshot path
  resolveSnapshotPath: (testPath, snapshotExtension) =>
    testPath.replace('__tests__', '__snapshots__') + snapshotExtension,

  // resolves from snapshot to test path
  resolveTestPath: (snapshotFilePath, snapshotExtension) =>
    snapshotFilePath
      .replace('__snapshots__', '__tests__')
      .slice(0, -snapshotExtension.length),

  // Example test path, used for preflight consistency check of the implementation above
  testPathForConsistencyCheck: 'some/__tests__/example.test.js',
};

```

