TITLE: Using Mock Functions with Array Filter
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use mock functions with array filtering to test functional continuation-passing style code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jestjs/jest/blob/main/docs/MockFunctions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
