TITLE: Configuring Jest Max Workers in GitHub Actions (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: Provides a YAML snippet for a GitHub Actions workflow. It uses the `SimenB/github-actions-cpu-cores` action to detect the number of available CPU cores in the runner environment and then passes this count to `jest --max-workers` to optimize parallel test execution time.
