TITLE: Testing with Automatic Mocking Enabled (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: A Jest test suite (`__tests__/automock.test.js`) demonstrating the behavior when the `automock: true` configuration option is set. It imports the `utils` module, verifies that its methods are automatically replaced with mock functions (`jest.fn()`), and shows how to provide custom mock implementations or return values using `.mockReturnValue()`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jestjs/jest/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-29.7/Configuration.md#2025-04-23_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
