TITLE: Defining a React Checkbox Component for DOM Testing (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: A functional React component (`CheckboxWithLabel`) written in TypeScript (`tsx`). It renders a checkbox input within a label. The label text changes between `labelOn` and `labelOff` props based on the checkbox's checked state, managed using the `useState` hook.
