TITLE: Complete Jest Test File with Class Mocking and Spying - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Presents a full test suite using a Jest module factory to mock a class, spy on its methods, and verify object instantiation and method calls. Demonstrates best practices in setup (mocking, beforeEach), test structure, and assertions. Dependencies include Jest and the tested modules. Expects the mocked module, method calls, and assertions with expected outputs.
