DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to test the `Users.all` method by mocking its `axios` dependency using `jest.mock('axios')`. `axios.get.mockResolvedValue(resp)` simulates a successful API response, allowing the test to verify the component's logic without actual network interaction. An alternative using `mockImplementation` is also commented.
