SOURCE: https://github.com/jestjs/jest/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-29.7/TutorialReact.md#2025-04-23_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
'use strict';\n\nconst {transform} = require('@babel/core');\nconst jestPreset = require('babel-preset-jest');\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  process(src, filename) {\n    const result = transform(src, {\n      filename,\n      presets: [jestPreset],\n    });\n\n    return result || src;\n  },\n};
```

